'''Ricardo Alexandre Almeida Santos''' (born 18 June 1995) is a [[Portuguese people|Portuguese]] professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Barnet F.C.|Barnet]].

==Playing career==
Santos was a youth team player at [[Dagenham & Redbridge F.C.|Dagenham & Redbridge]], making one appearance in the matchday squad,<ref>{{cite news|last=Munford|first=Colin|title=Former Daggers defender joins Peterborough United|url=http://www.barkinganddagenhampost.co.uk/sport/former_daggers_defender_joins_peterborough_united_1_3286595|accessdate=3 May 2014|newspaper=Barking and Dagenham Post|date=5 February 2014}}</ref> before he was released and signed by [[Thurrock F.C.|Thurrock]] manager [[Mark Stimson]], following a spell at [[Dover Athletic F.C.|Dover Athletic]] where he made no appearances.<ref>{{cite news|last=Munford|first=Colin|title=Former Daggers defender joins Peterborough United|url=http://www.barkinganddagenhampost.co.uk/sport/former_daggers_defender_joins_peterborough_united_1_3286595|accessdate=3 May 2014|newspaper=Barking and Dagenham Post|date=5 February 2014}}</ref> He impressed for the [[Isthmian League]] club, making 24 appearances,<ref>[http://www.pitchero.com/clubs/thurrock/teams/62466/player/ricardo-santos-1048749/29713 Ricardo Santos - Thurrock Football Club]</ref> and was signed by [[Peterborough United F.C.|Peterborough United]] manager [[Darren Ferguson]] on three-and-a-half-year contract in February 2014.<ref>{{cite news|title=Peterborough sign Portuguese defender Ricardo Santos|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26054753|accessdate=3 May 2014|newspaper=[[BBC Sport]]|date=5 February 2014}}</ref> He made his [[Football League One|League One]] debut on 3 May in a 0–0 draw with [[Port Vale F.C.|Port Vale]] at [[London Road Stadium|London Road]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Peterborough 0 - 0 Port Vale|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27167682|accessdate=3 May 2014|newspaper=[[BBC Sport]]|date=3 May 2014}}</ref> Santos scored his first goal for the club when he scored a late winner against [[Doncaster Rovers]] on 19 March 2016.<ref>{{cite news
|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35791527|title=Doncaster 1-2 Peterborough|publisher=[[BBC Sport]]|date=19 March 2016|accessdate=17 September 2016}}</ref> On 1 January 2017, Santos joined [[Barnet F.C.|Barnet]] for a fee of £100,000.<ref>[http://www.barnetfc.com/news/article/2016-17/barnet-complete-santos-signing-3492801.aspx Barnet complete Santos signing]</ref> He made his debut on the following day in a 1-0 win over [[Plymouth Argyle F.C.|Plymouth Argyle]].

